easuring cup, cook <nobr>2 min\/120°C\/\/speed 1<\/nobr>. Scrape base of mixing bowl with spatula to loosen rice.","Add hot stock, salt and pepper. Place Varoma dish into position and weigh in peas. Cover then cook <nobr>12-15 min\/100°C\/\/speed 1<\/nobr> until rice is cooked al dente (with a bite) - the risotto should be slightly soupy at this stage.","Set Varoma aside. Add reserved asparagus tips, reserved Parmesan and butter then stir in with spatula. Adjust seasoning if desired then replace Varoma and leave to rest for 2 minutes.","Serve with peas on the side accompanied by the tear and share rolls."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Preparation Before Demo","content":["250 g asparagus, woody ends removed"]},{"title":"Sun-dried Tomato Tear and Share Rolls","content":["220 g water","1 tsp sugar","2 tsp dried instant yeast","500 g strong white bread flour","90 g sun-dried tomatoes in oil, drained","30 g olive oil, plus extra for greasing","1 tsp fine sea salt, to taste"]},{"title":"Berry Foam","content":["80 - 140 g sugar, to taste","500 g mixed berries, frozen, to taste","10 - 30 g lime juice, to taste","1 egg white, from medium or large egg"]},{"title":"Baking","content":["1 egg yolk, from medium or large egg"]},{"title":"Asparagus Risotto","content":["60 g Parmesan cheese, cut in pieces (2 cm)","50 g shallots, halved","20 g olive oil","200 g dry white wine","250 g risotto rice","450 g vegetable stock, hot","½ tsp fine sea salt","¼ tsp ground black pepper","250 g frozen peas","20 g butter"]}],"id":"r218852","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-pyFan6LRmpo\/XZVPyX6UA-I\/AAAAAAAAc8k\/tXRP9IClVTA2tf7KzYEqyTl78VAH_ZL5wCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_EoH95SJlL_BhXmTk.png","title":"Asparagus Risotto, Sun-dried Tomato Tear and Share Rolls, Berry Foam","publishedAt":"2017-09-05T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"17.8 g","fat":"18.1 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"101.7 g","calories":"2758 kJ \/ 658 kcal"},"usefulItems":"bowl, serving bowls, large baking tray, freezer-